# Azure AI RAG Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    U[User] --> AGW[Application Gateway with WAF]
    AGW --> APP[App Service / Front End]
    APP --> ORCH[Orchestrator / Agent Layer]
    ORCH --> SEARCH[Azure AI Search]
    SEARCH --> ORCH
    ORCH --> APIM[API Management / AI Gateway]
    APIM --> AOAI[Azure OpenAI Model Deployment]
    AOAI --> ORCH
    ORCH --> APP
    APP --> U
```
